Package: bjpack1
Type: Package
Title: Create a table of performance measures, a ROC and PRC, and a shiny gadget of binary classifiers
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Bojung Seo <bjseo2@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Bojung Seo <bjseo2@gmail.com>
Description: Creates a table that includes all of the important performance 
        measures of classifier to intuitively provide important information 
        at once that is necessary for the comparison of the models' performance.
        Creates a ROC with useful information of the best model in a neat way.
        Creates a PRC for each model. 
        Creates a shiny gadget that provides a ROC/PRC according to a user's choice.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    flextable,
    ggplot2,
    InformationValue,
    magrittr,
    pROC,
    shiny,
    shinyWidgets
RoxygenNote: 7.2.2
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/qhwjd246/bjpack1
BugReports: https://github.com/qhwjd246/bjpack1/issues
